Class Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simpleaddressbook.Entry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Entry>

    public class Entry
extends Object
implements Comparable<Entry>, Serializable
    This class consists of methods to create, or make changes to, an Entry object to be used in the AddressBook class.
